8-16}}{{Dead link|date=March 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\n== Accolades ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Award Ceremony\n! Category\n! Recipient\n! Result\n! Ref.(s)\n|-\n| rowspan=3 | [[4th Mirchi Music Awards]]\n| [[Mirchi Music Award for Male Vocalist of The Year|Male Vocalist of The Year]]\n| [[Hans Raj Hans]] - \"Ik Tu Hi Tu Hi\"\n| rowspan=3 {{nom}}\n| rowspan=3 | <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.radiomirchi.com/mma2011/hindi/nominees.php|title=Nominations - Mirchi Music Award Hindi 2011|date=30 January 2013|access-date=24 May 2018|url-status=bot: unknown|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130130161203/http://www.radiomirchi.com/mma2011/hindi/nominees.php|archivedate=30 January 2013|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Mirchi Music Award for Upcoming Male Vocalist of The Year|Upcoming Male Vocalist of The Year]]\n| [[Shahid Mallya]] - \"Rabba Main Toh Mar Gaya Oye\"\n|-\n| Song representing Sufi tradition\n| \"Rabba Main Toh Mar Gaya Oye\"\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website|http://mausam-thefilm.com}}\n* {{IMDb title|1627924|Mausam}}\n* [http://www.cineindya.com/movies/mausam-2011/ Mausam Trailer HD: 'Mausam Movie Trailer and Reviews']\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110909093915/http://tiff.net/filmsandschedules/tiff/2011/mausam Mausam film page and review from Toronto International Film Festival (TIFF)]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mausam}}\n[[Category:2011 films]]\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2010s Hindi-language films]]\n[[Category:Indian war drama films]]\n[[Category:Indian aviation films]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Edinburgh]]\n[[Category:Films set in Jammu and Kashmir]]\n[[Category:Films featuring songs by Pritam]]\n[[Category:2010s war drama films]]\n[[Category:Indian Air Force in films]]\n[[Category:Films set in Kargil]]\n[[Category:Kashmir conflict in films]]\n[[Category:2011 directorial debut films]]\n", "name_user": "Jellysandwich0", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "/