Ia0UC&pg=PA530 530] |work=Movies in American History: An Encyclopedia |volume=1 |year=2011 |editor-first=Philip C. |editor-last=DiMare |publisher=ABC-CLIO |isbn=9781598842968}}</ref>\n* ''[[Seconds (1966 film)|Seconds]]'' (1966)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/movie/07D6BEA568|title=Seconds|publisher=|via=www.flickchart.com}}</ref>\n* ''[[The Shooting]]'' (1966)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/movie/F4BA5D6E79|title=The Shooting|publisher=|via=www.flickchart.com}}</ref>\n* ''[[Ride in the Whirlwind]]'' (1966)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/Charts.aspx?director=Monte+Hellman|title=The Best Movies Directed by Monte Hellman|website=Flickchart}}</ref>\n* ''[[You're a Big Boy Now]]'' (1966)<ref name=\"You're A Big Boy Now 1966\"/>\n* ''[[In the Heat of the Night (film)|In the Heat of the Night]]'' (1967)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/movie/461B82A158|title=In the Heat of the Night|publisher=|via=www.flickchart.com}}</ref>\n* ''[[Bonnie and Clyde (film)|Bonnie and Clyde]]'' (1967){{sfn|Thompson|Bordwell|2003|p=513}}{{sfn|Harris|2008|p=1\u20134}} \n* ''[[The Graduate]]'' (1967){{sfn|Thompson|Bordwell|2003|p=513}}{{sfn|Kr\u00e4mer|2005|p=8}}{{sfn|Harris|2008|p=1\u20134}}\n* ''[[In Cold Blood (film)|In Cold Blood]]'' (1967)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/movie/792FA8C48D|title=In Cold Blood|publisher=|via=www.flickchart.com}}</ref>\n* ''[[Reflections in a Golden Eye (film)|Reflections in a Golden Eye]]'' (1967)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/movie/B95D246070|title=Reflections in a Golden Eye|publisher=|via=www.flickchart.com}}</ref>\n* ''[[Cool Hand Luke]]'' (1967)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/Charts.aspx?actor=Paul+Newman|title=The Best Movies Starring Paul Newman|website=Flickchart}}</ref>\n* ''[[Who's That Knocking at My Door]]'' (1967)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickchart.com/movie/25C14B48CC|title=Who's That Knocking At My Door|publisher=|via=www.flickchart.com}}</ref>